sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Server

    Note over Client: State: CLOSED
    Note over Server: State: LISTEN

    Client->>Server: SYN (seq=1000, SYN=1)
    Note over Client: State: SYN_SENT
    Note over Server: Allocate TCB
    Server-->>Client: SYN-ACK (seq=5000, ack=1001, SYN=1, ACK=1)
    Note over Server: State: SYN_RECEIVED

    Client->>Server: ACK (seq=1001, ack=5001, ACK=1)
    Note over Client: State: ESTABLISHED
    Note over Server: State: ESTABLISHED

    Note over Client,Server: Data transfer begins
    Client->>Server: Data (seq=1001)
    Server-->>Client: ACK (ack=1001+data_len)

    Note over Client,Server: Connection Teardown
    Client->>Server: FIN (seq=N)
    Server-->>Client: ACK (ack=N+1)
    Server-->>Client: FIN (seq=M)
    Client->>Server: ACK (ack=M+1)
    Note over Client: TIME_WAIT (2xMSL)
